---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<section class="max-w-full bg-card border border-border rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 720 280" class="w-full h-auto">
    <!-- GitHub -> CodePipeline -->
    <line x1="120" y1="140" x2="200" y2="140" stroke="currentColor" class="text-border" />
    <!-- CodePipeline -> CodeBuild -->
    <line x1="320" y1="140" x2="400" y2="140" stroke="currentColor" class="text-border" />
    <!-- CodeBuild stem to fork -->
    <line x1="520" y1="140" x2="560" y2="140" stroke="currentColor" class="text-border" />
    <!-- Fork vertical -->
    <line x1="560" y1="50" x2="560" y2="230" stroke="currentColor" class="text-border" />
    <!-- Fork -> Lambda (top) -->
    <line x1="560" y1="50" x2="600" y2="50" stroke="currentColor" class="text-border" />
    <!-- Fork -> CloudFront (middle) -->
    <line x1="560" y1="140" x2="600" y2="140" stroke="currentColor" class="text-border" />
    <!-- Fork -> S3 (bottom) -->
    <line x1="560" y1="230" x2="600" y2="230" stroke="currentColor" class="text-border" />

    <foreignObject x="0" y="100" width="120" height="80">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
        <div class="w-8 h-8">
          <Icon name="tabler:brand-github" class="text-muted-foreground w-full h-full" />
        </div>
        <span class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground">GitHub</span>
      </div>
    </foreignObject>

    <foreignObject x="200" y="100" width="120" height="80">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12">
          <Icon name="logos:aws-codepipeline" class="w-full h-full" />
        </div>
        <span class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground">CodePipeline</span>
      </div>
    </foreignObject>

    <foreignObject x="400" y="100" width="120" height="80">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12">
          <Icon name="logos:aws-codebuild" class="w-full h-full" />
        </div>
        <span class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground">CodeBuild</span>
      </div>
    </foreignObject>

    <foreignObject x="600" y="10" width="120" height="80">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12">
          <Icon name="logos:aws-lambda" class="w-full h-full" />
        </div>
        <span class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground">Lambda (SSR)</span>
      </div>
    </foreignObject>

    <foreignObject x="600" y="100" width="120" height="80">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12">
          <Icon name="logos:aws-cloudfront" class="w-full h-full" />
        </div>
        <span class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground">CloudFront</span>
      </div>
    </foreignObject>

    <foreignObject x="600" y="190" width="120" height="80">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12">
          <Icon name="logos:aws-s3" class="w-full h-full" />
        </div>
        <span class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground">S3 (Assets)</span>
      </div>
    </foreignObject>
  </svg>
</section>

<p class="text-muted-foreground"><strong>GitHub</strong> triggers the pipeline on code changes. <strong>CodeBuild</strong> builds the framework and packages the SSR server for <strong>Lambda</strong> while uploading static assets to <strong>S3</strong>, then invalidates the <strong>CloudFront</strong> global cache to serve the latest version.</p>
